    "For instance, if a user asks, \"What are the monthly penalties across all contracts?",
    "\", the prompt instructs the Graph Agent to interpret the retrieved data and generate a bar chart.",
    "This visualization complements textual explanations, providing users with clearer insights into trends, comparisons, or aggregated data.",
    "By integrating visual responses, the system improves accessibility and interpretability, particularly for data-heavy queries.",
    "To illustrate this methodology, consider a scenario in Contract Management."
